answersResultList.title: You can be a flake.
answersResultList.resultContent: You want to follow through, but it doesn't always work out. Some days you're right on point. Some days you have no idea where the time goes. If you're trying to impress someone who's tripping on your flaws, good luck with that! Anyway, it's all about good intentions, right? You know that a real friend would forgive you.

answersResultList.title: You're not a flake.
answersResultList.resultContent: You're always where you say you'll be. Sometimes you're early. Your friends count on you, and your dates take you for granted - or assume you're really into them. If something comes up, you'll make a call so nobody's left hanging. Maybe the flakes in the world can learn from your example. Well, you can always hope!
